<paragraph blockId="43.[151,395,1656,1716]" box="[151,330,1692,1716]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,322,1692,1716]" captionStart="FIGURES 179–193" captionStartId="45.[151,263,1787,1810]" captionTargetBox="[166,1422,196,1760]" captionTargetId="figure-117@45.[151,1436,181,1774]" captionTargetPageId="45" captionText="FIGURES 179–193. Thrips species. T. palmi, female 179–183; (179) Head &amp; pronotum; (180) Antenna, right; (181) Metascutum; (182) Tergites VIII–X. T. palmi, male 183–184: (183) Tergites VIII–IX; (184) Sternite VI, sculpture omitted. T. pini, female 185–193: (185) Head &amp; pronotum; (186) Anteromedian area of head; (187) Antenna, right; (188) Metascutum; (189) Tergite VI &amp; pleurotergite, right side; (190) Tergites VIII–X; (191) Sternite VI. T. pini, male 192–193: (192) Tergites VIII–IX; (193) Sternite V, sculpture omitted." pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Figs. 179–184</figureCitation>
